name: Routine #5
description: Fast food. Fast food captures most of the market positions. It seems funny to me. As a person brought up in the era of fast food, I want to never remember this word again.   But if we look at this issue from the business side, we will understand that this is one of the greatest achievements , the genius of human thought. When you flip a coin, you have 2 sides. When one of them appears in front of you - don’t forget about another ...
